awn, cringe</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑδαρεῖ ς. φιλότητι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:798\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">798</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (anap.), cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:97\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">97</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr., s.v.l.); also <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. ποτὶ πάντας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:82\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.82</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ς. ποτὶ ἀγγελίαν</foreign> greet it with joy, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">O.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.6</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n93056.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. pers., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fawn upon</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κέρκῳ τινά</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1031\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1031</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl defau